snippet.textDisplay:
i remember before all the memes and challenges, you were just a dude who liked to play bass. i’ve been subbed since early 2017, when i was an awkward teen who had no idea what he wanted to do with his life, and your talents were so fun to watch that it made me want to pick up the bass guitar. my mother got me a bass that christmas, and it was one of the best presents i ever got. (still can’t slapp tho 😤)

fast forward almost 3 years, and you’ve evolved from that shy italian guy into a legit content creator and a force to be reckoned with on youtube. i bought an amp and some production equipment, and i plan to start recording and releasing my own music soon. i hope the next decade holds great things for me, as i’m only 20 and have my whole life ahead of me, but i would be lying if i didn’t wish you the best too. happy new year davie, and i hope that the next decade of your life (and ours) is the best. 👍
